{"tid":1002941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭枕吧女胸　警笑容滿面","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T10:32:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13a6ddb82f37e4ee5d575187a5cd9269efa4651a","tid":1002941,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20603131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20603131&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6uaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=0af69ec0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20603131&h=bb00af8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20603131</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月31日 <br />\n<br />\n頭枕吧女胸　警笑容滿面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190131/large/a0402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190131%2Flarge%2Fa0402a.gif&h=1f600a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【請食「波餅」】吧女玩得興起，將放蛇警的面部拉貼自己胸部。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】從警方去年6月22日第五次到涉案酒吧放蛇的閉路電視片段可見，有吧女臂纏放蛇警員的頸，將他的頭拉到自己胸部上，該警員枕完胸部「獲釋」坐直時笑容滿面。有男警更伸手到坐在對面、打扮中性的女警胸前，疑似有所動作。該女警陶麗瑩周二供稱，當晚她和男同袍玩一模一樣的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n片中放蛇警員一行六人，在涉案酒吧內的長枱就座後不久，便有八名打扮性感的泰籍吧女梅花間竹地坐在警員身邊，其間一名曾放蛇四次的男警先離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒吧負責人管理賣淫場所囚八月警放蛇多次揸胸　紫藤轟濫權<br />\n<br />\n女警同玩遊戲<br />\n<br />\n吧女一開始便主動與眾警閒聊，又不時擺動身體，對他們輕觸又依偎；警員起初有點拘謹，未有大動作。<br />\n<br />\n其後有吧女把頭埋在警員褲襠，另一名吧女隨即大力按住該吧女的頭，警員狀甚愉快，亦有吧女捉住警員的手，放在自己胸上。有警員與吧女猜枚輸了，將「換領券」塞入吧女乳溝，吧女立即大笑，女警稍後又將頭枕在身旁吧女胸上。片段中可見，枱上有三支黑牌威士忌空樽，另有其他飲料，又見有警員全程在室內吸煙。最終同袍到場採取拘捕行動，吧女狀甚驚惶，放蛇警員則表現冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭語霆  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n酒吧負責人管理賣淫場所囚八月　警放蛇多次揸胸紫藤轟濫權<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n曾接種疫苗　少女流感併發肺炎命危"},{"pid":"3f6fcc909023b031f2ca62c6fe9b80180ffbda82","tid":1002941,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"做差佬真好"},{"pid":"117917aabf5bb00ade3accb866da1227a46d1a4a","tid":1002941,"uid":31200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"仲可以出公數 有得玩有酒飲 毅進仔幾爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0231e7ee58f34baaa5f33ca0b87c0b51dcc7af6e","tid":1002941,"uid":228963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa474426decddc08abce5e8a64f95c84b967f964","tid":1002941,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:09:07.000Z","msg":"點先可以入職去放蛇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37d623fcc0ec634ed99c9c7c53d8f3957906140","tid":1002941,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"條女好似幾樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d025f53fd55fc4aaa5b9fcbc2707ea7de04a31e","tid":1002941,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"唔通喊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857d3f5567f1a1c5934ca3e58553a4697468357f","tid":1002941,"uid":6222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:11:15.000Z","msg":"考警個陣同阿sir講有豐富叫雞同夜場經驗係咪會優先考慮同做埋放蛇工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3a5d3e0